Rating: 4
Far, far Easier than Pie!! I only used 1/2 cup of sugar and 3 tbsp lemon juice, about 1" of stick butter...and the 1 tbsp of vanilla. I cooked them about 20 minutes in the oven...it is possible to burn the sugar, so stir it every 4-5 minutes, and keep an eye on the color...dark is not as tasty! Vanilla ice cream with the extra sauce is all you need!

